{"tid":786971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 傳政府本周內推培訓科技人才計劃 專才每月可獲3.2萬資助","createTime":"2018-08-20T10:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T09:07:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"99084022d31fbd6b2b2aeea696e6609b1cf508e2","tid":786971,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"星島日報》今日引述消息報道指，政府本周再推出「科技專才培育計劃」及「再工業化及科技培訓計劃」，加強本地人才培訓。政府去年發表《施政報告》及今年公布《財政預算案》，提到有關計劃於今年下半年落實，包括推出「博士專才庫」，每名專才每月最高可獲3.2萬元，資助期長達兩年；「再工業化及科技培訓計劃」則由職業訓練局負責審批先進製造技術課程，消息稱「生產力局及應科院將加入計劃，為工業4.0、智能製造、人工智能等多項先進技術授課」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180820/58584940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584940&d=LaYFzeWo0jmsFzezrbAsB3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=cf85ada3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584940&h=42738fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180820/58584940</a>"},{"pid":"f56bdb3099da6ede016b9291f906c9a4dbf1c897","tid":786971,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"老貓你做科技9 up人才都有三皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970314dc023021c0e18a4dc2127af55a2353ea6a","tid":786971,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"We are IT專材 family<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www1.picturepush.com/photo/a/8133409/640/8133409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.picturepush.com%2Fphoto%2Fa%2F8133409%2F640%2F8133409.jpg&h=ab07aa29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"242640ce6f4754f1494418383fb9543ba6f89bfe","tid":786971,"uid":54733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"科技專才黎香港做地盤、賣保險?"},{"pi